node.text: Looking like a hell of a back workout! Keep on with the good work man 💪

Today’s Pull Day making it the second this week. Some solid lifts here.
-
🎇LAT Pulldown x DB Row
4s  12|10|8|6r  4s 12-15r
🎆Arnold Press x Single Arm Front Raises
4s  8-10r  x  4s  12-15r
🎇Seated Cable Rows [3 sec hold] x Kneeling Rope Facepulls
4s  8-10r  x  4s  12r
🎆SM Shrugs x Seated DB Flys#4s  25|20|20|20 x  4s  12r
🎇Standing Single Arm Preacher Curls x Single Arm Hammer Curls
4s  15|12|10|8  x  4s  12r
🎆Abs (not filmed)
-

Be sure before each workout always stretch, get warmed up, and then begin, and don’t forget to stretch after! Hydrate during the day, especially if you’re taking creatine or any supplement. If you have any questions or comments drop em below and I’ll do what I can to answer them.
-
